FOR EACH company–opportunity pair:
│
├─ Signal 1: sectors_overlap(comp_sector, opp_sector, ontology)?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "sector_overlap" to pass_labels)
│
├─ Signal 2: comp_sector in adjacent_value_chain_sectors?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "value_chain_adjacent")
│
├─ Signal 3: keyword_match_count(capability_keywords, comp_profile+products) ≥ 2?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "capability_keywords:N")
│
├─ Signal 4: keyword_match_count(required_inputs, comp_products) ≥ 1?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "input_overlap:N")
│
├─ Signal 5: sim_struct_product[ci,oi] ≥ 0.80?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "signal_product_sim:X.XXX")
│
├─ Signal 6: sim_profile[ci,oi] ≥ 0.82?
│  └─ YES → PASS (add "signal_profile_sim:X.XXX")
│
└─ If ANY signal fires:
   ├─ _send_to_gpt = True
   ├─ triage_pass = True
   ├─ triage_reason = formatted pass_labels
   └─ → Route to GPT Step 6
   
   Else:
   ├─ _send_to_gpt = False
   ├─ triage_pass = False
   ├─ ai_decision = "Filtered"
   ├─ triage_reason = "signal values: overlap=X, adj=X, kw=X, inp=X, sig_p=X, sig_pf=X"
   └─ → Skip GPT, count as n_filtered
